<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-08-19T04:30:54.991569+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>dece6a4b536099d907d7b665e2deae7e</id><title>H按息率回升至3.31厘 僅差封頂息19點子 業界：超低息蜜月期完結</title><updated>2025-08-18T19:28:07+08:00</updated><author><name>驚青猛男</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-18T19:28:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573647133"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573647133"&gt;H按息率回升至3.31厘 僅差封頂息19點子 業界：超低息蜜月期完結&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隨着金管局12度入市買港元後，銀行體系總結餘已回落至約537億元，重返接近金管局5月初入市前水平，港元拆息（HIBOR）隨之回升，本周一更已重越2厘水平之上，報2.01393厘，創逾3個月新高。若以一般H按「H+1.3厘」計，H按實際按息已回升至3.31厘，僅比封頂息率3.5厘輕微低出19點子。有業內人士更直言，「超低息蜜月期」已完結。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3491347/" target="_blank" uhash="ccbc491a7269e5ef83c987fc5a18876d"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3491347/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32010487&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=147412198068a3fdff26c7a7_14627861"/><published>2025-08-18T19:28:07+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>00e41f2226441259352e4d4b84d9839e</id><title>居屋2024揀樓完結 5新居屋及重售單位售罄 原文網址: 居屋2024揀樓完結 5新居屋及重售單位售罄 租置公屋賣剩20間 | 香港01 https://ww</title><updated>2025-08-18T19:50:55+08:00</updated><author><name>~kurapika~</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-18T19:50:55+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573647391"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573647391"&gt;「居屋2024」5月31日開始選樓，今期推售5個發展項目共7,132個新居屋單位及約300個重售居屋單位，在53天內已經全部售罄。整體銷售時間比「居屋2023」快約三成，反映申請者對資助出售單位的需求持續殷切。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 居屋2024揀樓完結5新居屋及重售單位售罄租置公屋賣剩20間 | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60230111%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=39bb92966403457c26358559f443ae76&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;火速去貨&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32010500&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=147412198068a3fdff26c7a7_14627861"/><published>2025-08-18T19:50:55+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f08179011a8d173c4fce9398608e0cfd</id><title>一手新盤開價愈來愈進取</title><updated>2025-08-19T03:40:52+08:00</updated><author><name>雨中進擊的妹妹</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T03:40:52+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573650992"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573650992"&gt;證明樓市見底&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;早三個月無買已錯失低位&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32010728&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=147412198068a3fdff26c7a7_14627861"/><published>2025-08-19T03:40:52+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f5005ae97f885dcf52b42c3497ffc1d8</id><title>4000萬收$73000 租 , 笑死人咩</title><updated>2025-08-19T10:14:09+08:00</updat